# Git commits

- All commit messages (subject + optional body) must be written in **English**.
- Prefer imperative, clear subjects (e.g. `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`).

## Three remotes (required when publishing)

This repo is expected to have **three remotes**:

1. `git push gitlab <branch>`
2. `git push github <branch>`
3. `git push forgejo <branch>`

Do not consider work “published” until all three pushes succeed, unless explicitly instructed otherwise.

